{"THEW":[{"def":"Manner; custom; habit; form of behavior; qualities of mind; disposition; specifically, good qualities; virtues.","pos":""},{"def":"Muscle or strength; nerve; brawn; sinew.","pos":""}],"THEWED":[{"def":"Furnished with thews or muscles; as, a well-thewed limb.","pos":""},{"def":"Accustomed; mannered.","pos":""}],"THEWY":[{"def":"Having strong or large thews or muscles; muscular; sinewy; strong.","pos":""}]}